性的有机氟化物 (PFAS)。 据报道，此次调查从 5 月下旬持续到 9 月下旬，调查对象包括供水人口超过 5000 人的上水道和 101 至 5000 人的简易自来水管道等，具体检测的是净水场的出口水和水龙头出水的水质。 报道称，此次检查的自来水管道共 1745 个，在其中的 332 个管道都检测出了有机氟化物，涉及日本全国 47 个都道府县中的 46 个，这也是日本首次专门针对有机氟化物的全国大规模调查。 据此前报道，有机氟化物是上千种化学物质的总称，这类物质难以降解，会在人体和环境中积累，因此又被称为「永久性化学物」。美国疾病控制和预防中心 (CDC) 的分支机构美国有毒物质和疾病登记局表示，这些物质可能导致包括肾癌、睾丸癌、胆固醇水平升高等一系列健康问题。日本大量自来水管道检出致癌物"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-0da075d2e8c7a95492f91ec616185ad5_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5559507592"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIppSrxcebtNIMEAMaCTExMjA4ODQyMCD/5Kq6BjAAOJUDQAlyCjU1NTk1MDc1OTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1733014983.592900", "card_id": "Q_5446091525", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "小草包横扫 Doinb 队后发朋友圈锐评「比打单简单」，Doinb 还有机会复出吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f0f47b147a8d2612ad7d592df9061c25_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.7 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5446091525"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIppSrxcebtNIMEAMaCTExMjA2NTczOCD7i6S6BjAAODVACnIKNTQ0NjA5MTUyNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1733014983.593266", "card_id": "Q_5553796384", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 149}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "体操冠军吴柳芳、击剑冠军秦雪被曝当网红擦边，退役运动员转型面临哪些问题？体育产业化发展是否存在不足？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-12f2e82e436bd3779167ef5facfb28a6_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "2.8 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""},